{
  "title": "Springy Sweet Peruvian Fish Ceviche Clasico",
  "description": "A refreshing and light Peruvian dish featuring succulent fish marinated in a zesty mixture, perfect for a springtime meal",
  "cuisine": "Peruvian",
  "diet": [
